    "min_value": 30,
    "max_value": 70,
    "mode": "range",
    "include_min": true,
    "include_max": true
  },
  {
    "label": "High",
    "condition_type": "GTE",
    "min_value": 70,
    "mode": "range",
    "include_min": true
  }
]
```

**Condition Types:**
- `LTE` - Less Than or Equal (requires `max_value`)
- `GTE` - Greater Than or Equal (requires `min_value`)
- `BTW` - Between (requires both `min_value` and `max_value`)

